        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Items</head>
                <p xml:id="del-2022-05-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T22:50:48.561+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-de-0ec6022d">(just as) Jie and Zhou were not completely bad."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T22:50:57.234+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-de-0ec6022d">"Yao and Shun were not completely good </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T22:58:09.357+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Wei Wendi sagt:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T22:58:10.695+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Wei Wendi sagtw:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T22:59:43.466+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Wei Wendi sagte:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:14:59.38+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and already had an</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:19:12.805+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">they knew in their heart</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:19:49.727+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">they knew in their heart which (parts) </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:23:42.385+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">teaching and instruction</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:33:38.255+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">"I know about the acts of Yao and Shun."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:38:07.254+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">"It is not stupid that the scholars don't talk about</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:40:03.274+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">However, they were constrained by rites als law</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:40:46.647+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and although their mouths could not express it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:45:53.169+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">teaching and instruction.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:46:14.26+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and these teaching and instruction.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:48:13.305+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">This is why Mengzi states:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:49:41.178+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">The worthies of former times also looked at these (for instruction)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:50:15.031+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">All these also show that the worthies of former times also looked at these (for instruction)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:51:31.145+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">However, they were constrained by rites and law</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:51:37.037+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and these limitation were applied to teaching and instruction.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:51:45.088+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">they knew in their heart which (parts) were not right,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:52:03.654+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">of which there turned out to be a lot.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:53:43.947+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Thus, he called good what was good on the basis of its goodness, </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:56:04.25+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">did not criticise it any more (than necessary);</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-02T23:56:23.34+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">should not be praised any more (than necessary).</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:10:55.235+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Then, as regards the historiographical work of Lu, the Chunqiu,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:13:37.305+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Then, as regards the historiographical work of Lu, the Chunqiu, (it twisted the facts)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:13:44.31+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">for the sake of (protecting the image of) the worthies on the outside</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:13:45.781+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and for the sake of the inside (stability) of the state itself.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:19:10.294+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">the facts were twisted</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:20:30.461+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">the facts were twisted and rougly woven,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T00:21:04.656+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and all the actions were </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T06:25:38.973+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">"As for words: It is not stupid that the scholars don't talk about</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-5a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-03T06:26:32.655+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">"It is not stupid that the scholars don't talk about</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:21:49.513+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Thus</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:22:14.027+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:25:29.811+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">They are all like this</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:38:01.229+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:47:21.992+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that) Jie of the Xia</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:52:21.189+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and that the King of Wu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T17:53:05.56+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and that the King of Wu beheaded </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:16:00.264+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and (they show that) </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:17:09.69+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and (they show that those who commit) butchery</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:17:28.659+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">Note:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:18:19.28+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">These events are from the "Book of Zhou".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:27:01.677+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">The "Documents of the Zou" are the remainder of those of the "Shangshu"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:28:43.474+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">The "Documents of the Zou" are the remainder of those of the "Shangshu" that Confucius excluded</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:35:30.49+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When one </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:36:04.62+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:36:34.322+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine how Confucius</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:36:49.061+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">This being so, what need is there for the Chunqiu,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:36:50.432+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine how Confucius established the Rites (in the "Chunqiu")</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:38:59.152+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that) </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:43:51.602+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and (that)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:46:55.507+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and (that) evilness and ??? do not end.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:48:08.519+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">however (the Chunqiu), with a bostful brush and splendid words,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:50:00.373+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">states that "</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:58:21.98+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">are about </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:58:56.281+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine how Confucius revised the "Shijing",</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T18:59:00.182+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine the "Shijing" as revised by Confucius revised,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:01:08.167+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine the "Shijing" as revised by Confucius,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:01:25.95+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that) all the (songs of) "Guo Feng"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:01:52.55+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">contain criticism and reprimands</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:03:44.159+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine Confucius eliminated (parts of) the "Shijing",</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:03:45.614+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">When we examine howConfucius eliminated (parts of) the "Shijing",</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:08:43.977+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that) </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:11:08.73+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">(we see that) the ruler takes a bride from Wu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:11:46.825+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and calls her his family,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:16:55.697+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">but when the Minister of Justice asked him about it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:17:12.739+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">he responded that it was because he "knew about the Rites".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:17:29.594+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">but when the Sheriff (of Chen) asked Confucius about it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:18:40.398+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and that when the Sheriff (of Chen) asked Confucius,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:19:23.732+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">he responded that it was because he "understood ritual propriety".</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:23:27.476+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001">論語 / 7 《述而篇第七》</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2o0001_tls_039-7a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#Lea.Wallraff" modified="2022-05-04T19:23:43.618+09:00" resp-del="#Lea.Wallraff" src-id="KR2o0001-en-20a79bf9">and refers to her as (part of) his clan,</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
</TEI>